Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.29,0:05:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 但是重點是 - 短笛 短笛遜爆了\N{\fs38}- But the point is... - Piccolo? Ugh, piccolo sucks.
