Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.83,0:05:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說 短笛就是小一號的長笛\N{\fs38}I mean, piccolo is basically like a tiny flute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想玩正常尺寸的東西\N{\fs38}I wanted to play real-sized things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 你就該這么著\N{\fs38}Of course you did, and you should've.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.03,0:05:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是為什么 你能懂真是太好了\N{\fs38}That's why it's... it's so great that you get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.03,0:06:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我懂什么了 - 我的藝術 我\N{\fs38}- What do I get? - My art. Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.54,0:06:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎 我要用我的課題向你致敬\N{\fs38}You know what? I'm gonna dedicate my project to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就叫它"爸爸的小短笛"\N{\fs38}I'll call it "Dad's piccolo."
