Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我猜猜 所以是兩頁的A 72頁的B咯\N{\fs38}So let me guess. 2 "A"S and 72 "B"S.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.04,0:06:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給那個\N{\fs38}Well, I gave a "C" To the
