Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs36}<紅字>電影1995年的版本女主角是黛米摩爾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你和Eve聊得怎么樣了 - 這個\N{\fs38}- How'd your talk with Eve go? - Well, it was, uh... it, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個\N{\fs38}Uh... wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你干了什么好事 - 啥都沒有 真的什么都沒做\N{\fs38}- What did you do? - I did nothing. I literally did nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一分鐘前我還在讓她別太這么激進\N{\fs38}I-I-one minute, I'm talking to her about being less edgy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一分鐘她就要用課題向我致敬了\N{\fs38}And the next minute, she's dedicating the project to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.98,0:06:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道該讓我來和她談的\N{\fs38}I knew I should've done this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你太愛他們了 - 是的 這是個大問題\N{\fs38}- You love them too much. - I do. It's a real problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸媽肯定會這么說\N{\fs38}You know, my parents would've just said,
