Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.75,0:07:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們顯然不能這么做\N{\fs38}Well, that's clearly not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 她會自覺停止\N{\fs38}Okay, I got it. She is going to stop on her own
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我要好好嚇唬嚇唬她\N{\fs38}because I am going to scare her straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她得聽聽Carley Steiner的故事\N{\fs38}She needs to hear the story of Carley Steiner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是Carley Steiner\N{\fs38}Who's Carley Steiner?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.94,0:07:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我高中的同學\N{\fs38}She's a girl I went to high school with,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她為了個表演把頭發都剪了\N{\fs38}and she cut off all of her hair in a performance piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當頭發長回來的時候 變得又粗又怪\N{\fs38}And then when it grew back, it was all stumpy and weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給這個故事加點料 來點海洛因的情節\N{\fs38}I'm gonna jazz it up a little and throw some heroin in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這肯定行 肯定行\N{\fs38}Oh, that'll work. That will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你這么快就趕來了\N{\fs38}Thanks for joining me on such short notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.62,0:07:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你餓了么  我能湊合做碗湯\N{\fs38}Um, are you hungry? I could scare up some soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得有點男人的擔當\N{\fs38}I had to be a man and just
