Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是吧 這是我的房間\N{\fs38}but you're in my room, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還借你我的緊身牛仔褲\N{\fs38}And to think I lent you my skinny jeans.
