Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:17:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 親愛的 我只是個男人\N{\fs38}No, honey. I'm just a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我照片在這兒呢\N{\fs38}There's my photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看上去年輕了二十歲\N{\fs38}Wow, you look 20 years younger.
