Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說 這看上去才討喜\N{\fs38}Hey, I mean that's more... like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 帶上快走\N{\fs38}Okay, just grab it, and let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的 不能只拿這幅啊\N{\fs38}Well, honey, we can't just take that one,
