Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.36,0:18:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 往那邊去點  - 是 看出來了\N{\fs38}- Walk that way a little bit. - Oh, yeah, yeah, I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑\N{\fs38}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.81,0:18:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們真是太難以置信了 你們說過沒啥的\N{\fs38}I can't believe you guys! You said you were cool with it.
