Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.71,0:18:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么不行\N{\fs38}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 這是個好問題  - 而我們也有了好答案\N{\fs38}- It was a good question. - And we finally had a good answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 因為我們這么說了  - 什么\N{\fs38}- Because we said so. - What?
