Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這大概持續了二十分鐘\N{\fs38}This went on for 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們說遍了教育書里的陳詞濫調\N{\fs38}We hit every parenting cliche in the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就得這么著\N{\fs38}And that's the way it's gonna be
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你還生活在我們屋檐下\N{\fs38}as long as you're living under our roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們太差勁了\N{\fs38}You guys are so lame!
