Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗碗機不是玩具\N{\fs38}The dishwasher is not a toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的對 我錯了 對不起\N{\fs38}You're right, I'm wrong, I'm sorry.
